battle of the sexes is an upcoming american sports comedy-drama film directed by jonathan dayton and valerie faris and written by simon beaufoy . the plot is loosely based on the 1973 tennis match between billie jean king and bobby riggs . the film stars emma stone , steve carell , andrea riseborough , elisabeth shue , austin &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; , and sarah silverman . the film is scheduled to be screened at the 2017 toronto international film festival . the film is scheduled to be released on september 22 , 2017 , by fox searchlight pictures . it is rated pg-13 for " some sexual content and partial nudity " , making it the first &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; rated film directed by jonathan dayton and valerie faris .